    <span class="govuk-caption-xl gem-c-title__context">
      Guidance
    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    The eCommerce Directive after the transition period
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">At the end of the transition period, the eCommerce Directive will no longer apply to the UK. You should begin to prepare for these changes now.
</p>

  </div>
</div>

